Description_lang: Your healing has a chance to apply Bramble Barrier to your target, absorbing $425838s2 damage and causing $425838s5 Nature damage to attackers when struck. If the barrier is broken, the target is healed for ${$425838s4*($426321d/$426321t1)} over $426321d. If it expires without breaking, the target gains $425838s3 Versatility for $426322d.
